class CommentType(str, Enum):
    """Class representing the different types of important comments."""

    TODO = "TODO"
    FIXME = "FIXME"
    NOTE = "NOTE"
    HACK = "HACK"
    XXX = "XXX"
    REVIEW = "REVIEW"
    OPTIMIZE = "OPTIMIZE"
    CHANGED = "CHANGED"
    QUESTION = "QUESTION"
    Q = "Q"
    DEPRECATED = "@deprecated"
    NOSONAR = "NOSONAR"
    TODO_FIXME = "TODO-FIXME"

    def __str__(self) -> str:
        return self.value
